# What is this
This is a video tile upscaler by only using comfyui-easy-node. This workflow utilizes for loop nodes, which makes this workflow quite versatile (and might be confusing) that you can adapt and work with it. You can even adapt this workflow using native version instead, or use Fun/VACE/Context windows/any extensions wrapper can support. 

## Why not use Ultimate SD Upscaler (USDU) instead?
It's a good upscaler, but only works on native. This workflow utilize WanVideoWrapper nodes by kijai, which in my opinion upscales better.

Also, USDU has a flickering bug when enabling `tiled decode`. This improves quality, but the flickering is annoying for me.
